article_title: Displaced people reportedly killed in Rafah air strike.
sentence: Displaced  people  reportedly  killed  in  Rafah  air  strike.

article_title: Displaced people reportedly killed in Rafah air strike.
sentence: Palestinian  media  report  that  at  least  18  people,  including  nine  children  and  several  women,  were  killed  in  an  overnight  Israeli  air  strike  on  a  residential  building  on  the  outskirts  of  the  southern  city  of  Rafah.

article_title: Displaced people reportedly killed in Rafah air strike.
sentence: Another  video  taken  by  Eslayeh  outside  al-Najjah  hospital  in  Rafah  showed  mourners  watching  as  men  laid  the  bodies  of  those  killed  on  the  ground.
